original_title: Stan Getz Quartet: Live at Montreux 1972
overview: In his first appearance at the Montreux Jazz Festival, Stan Getz and his quartet explore the fusion side of jazz. Tracks include "Captain Marvel," "Day Waves," "Lush Life," "Windows," "La Fiesta" and more.
title: Stan Getz Quartet: Live at Montreux 1972
